# libFuzzer runtime artifacts (sha-named files) — auto-generated.
# Only seed_*.json/topo in this tree should be versioned.
#
# Ignore every top-level entry, then allow-list the .gitignore itself,
# named seeds, and the two structured subdirs (whose own non-seed
# contents are ignored just below).
/*
!.gitignore
!seed_*
!symbol-table/
!backend-request/
symbol-table/*
!symbol-table/seed_*
backend-request/*
!backend-request/seed_*
